  "page": "A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms - Season 1",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> This article or section is a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stub\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help \"A Wiki Of Ice And Fire\" by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_-_Season_1&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a> and/or improving existing text.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\"><i>A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</i></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nSeason 1</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">No. of episodes</span></th><td>\n6<sup id=\"cite_ref-Harris_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Harris-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Begin_Production_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Begin_Production-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Country of origin</span></th><td>\nUnited States</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Network</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HBO\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:HBO\">HBO</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Release</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Original run</th><td>\n2025<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Season chronology</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;border:none;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_episodes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"List of A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms episodes (page does not exist)\">List of episodes</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Season 1</b> of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_(TV_series)\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms (TV series)\">A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</a></i> is the first season of the series. This season is an adaptation of the first <a href=\"/index.php/Dunk_and_Egg\" title=\"Dunk and Egg\">Dunk and Egg</a> novella, <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>, that takes place at <a href=\"/index.php/Ashford\" title=\"Ashford\">Ashford</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a> during the late reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Plot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Plot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Crew\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Crew</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Cast\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cast</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Starring\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Starring</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Additional_cast\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Additional cast</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Episodes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Episodes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Plot\">Plot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_-_Season_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Plot\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><i>The Hedge Knight</i> centers around the <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Dunk</a> and his young <a href=\"/index.php/Knight#Pages_and_Squires\" title=\"Knight\">squire</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Egg</a>, 90 years before the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Crew\">Crew</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_-_Season_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Crew\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<p><b>Showrunner</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ira Parker</li></ul>\n<p><b>Writers</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ira Parker</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/George_R.R._Martin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"George R.R. Martin\">George R.R. Martin</a></li>\n<li>Hiram Martinez</li>\n<li>Annie Julie Wyman</li>\n<li>Aziza Barnes</li></ul>\n<p><b>Directors</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sarah_Adina_Smith\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Sarah Adina Smith\">Sarah Adina Smith</a> <small>(3 episodes)</small><sup id=\"cite_ref-Begin_Production_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Begin_Production-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Owen_Harris_(director)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Owen Harris (director)\">Owen Harris</a> <small>(3 episodes)</small><sup id=\"cite_ref-Begin_Production_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Begin_Production-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>Executive producers</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>George R.R. Martin</li>\n<li>Ira Parker</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ryan_Condal\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ryan Condal\">Ryan Condal</a></li>\n<li>Vince Gerardis</li>\n<li>Hiram Martinez</li>\n<li>Annie Julie Wyman</li>\n<li>Aziza Barnes</li>\n<li>Owen Harris</li>\n<li>Sarah Bradshaw</li></ul>\n<p><b>Producer</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ti Mikkel</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cast\">Cast</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_-_Season_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Cast\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Main article: <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_actors_of_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"List of actors of A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms\">List of actors of A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</a></div>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"List of characters created for A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms (page does not exist)\">List of characters created for A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</a></div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Starring\">Starring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_-_Season_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Starring\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\"><img alt=\"Dunk.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/78/Dunk.svg/16px-Dunk.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/78/Dunk.svg/24px-Dunk.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/78/Dunk.svg/32px-Dunk.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Claffey\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Peter Claffey\">Peter Claffey</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Dunk</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/16px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/24px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dexter_Sol_Ansell\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dexter Sol Ansell\">Dexter Sol Ansell</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Egg</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Additional_cast\">Additional cast</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_-_Season_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Additional cast\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Aerion_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerion Targaryen\"><img alt=\"Aerion Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/32/Aerion_Targaryen.svg/16px-Aerion_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/32/Aerion_Targaryen.svg/24px-Aerion_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/32/Aerion_Targaryen.svg/32px-Aerion_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Finn_Bennett\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Finn Bennett\">Finn Bennett</a> as Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aerion_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerion Targaryen\">Aerion Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Begin_Production_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Begin_Production-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/20px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/30px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/40px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Wade Briggs as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Crakehall_(Kingsguard)\" title=\"Roland Crakehall (Kingsguard)\">Roland Crakehall</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/16px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/24px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertie_Carvel\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Bertie Carvel\">Bertie Carvel</a> as Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Targaryen_(son_of_Daeron_II)\" title=\"Baelor Targaryen (son of Daeron II)\">Baelor Taragryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Begin_Production_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Begin_Production-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Tanzyn Crawford as <a href=\"/index.php/Tanselle\" title=\"Tanselle\">Tanselle</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Begin_Production_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Begin_Production-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/16px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/24px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/32px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Ings\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Daniel Ings\">Daniel Ings</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Baratheon\" title=\"Lyonel Baratheon\">Lyonel Baratheon</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Begin_Production_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Begin_Production-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maekar_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maekar I Targaryen\"><img alt=\"Maekar Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/94/Maekar_Targaryen.svg/16px-Maekar_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/94/Maekar_Targaryen.svg/24px-Maekar_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/94/Maekar_Targaryen.svg/32px-Maekar_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sam_Spruell\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Sam Spruell\">Sam Spruell</a> as Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maekar_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maekar I Targaryen\">Maekar Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Begin_Production_2-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Begin_Production-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hardyng\" title=\"House Hardyng\"><img alt=\"House Hardyng.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/16px-House_Hardyng.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/24px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/32px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ross Anderson as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Hardyng\" title=\"Humfrey Hardyng\">Humfrey Hardyng</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\"><img alt=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/16px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/24px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/32px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_Ashley_(English_actor)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Edward Ashley (English actor)\">Edward Ashley</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">Steffon Fossoway</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Variety_cast_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Variety_cast-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Daeron Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\"><img alt=\"Daeron Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4b/Daeron_Targaryen.svg/16px-Daeron_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4b/Daeron_Targaryen.svg/24px-Daeron_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4b/Daeron_Targaryen.svg/32px-Daeron_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henry_Ashton_(actor)\" class=\"extiw\" 